sentence: died: june 12, 2015 william charles claar, age 65, passed away friday, june 12, 2015 at the kobacker house.
bill grew up in jackson, oh. he is a longtime employee of worthington industries.
preceded in death by parents, william and myrtle claar.

survived by daughter, mechele (danny) catcher; 2 1/2 grandchildren, daniel and kyle catcher and their little sibling on the way; sister, sara ""darlene"" claar-swan; nieces, teresa rollings and tonya swan; great nephews, billy rollings and todd swan.
a celebration of bill's life will be held at a later date.
bill's family encourages memorial contributions in his memory be made to home.
reach hospice - kobacker house or the american cancer society.
arrangements with the tidd family funeral home.
